Zm_arctic_escape_v1
By -Mac D-
No. Of Players : 64

Here is an escape map made by me, inspired by Island Escape and Boat Escape.

Maps already been tested and doesnt have any major bugs.

Ive decided to release the .vmf file in this release which you can find in the zip file.  You MAY edit, change, remix the map as you like, but you MUST leave the MacD introduction screen in the map.  You MAY put your name in the introduction screen as an editor of the map if you make a remix of it.
